Name: Mr. Parkour
About the game: 'Mr. Parkour' is a 2d arcade parkour platformer game. Run through dangerous levels, jump through enemies and leave obstacles behind you. 60 levels of crushing difficulty, driving soundtrack, a sea of enemies and traps! Can you get to the end without breaking your keyboard or gamepad? Then you are a real parkourist! But be careful, the enemies are everywhere and they do not sleep.. Game Features: - 60 levels with increasing difficulty - Old school gameplay - Nice pixel art graphics - Control your character using the keyboard or the gamepad
